messages.content: Could we please set up a time to speak at least briefly?
Wanting to follow up on this

We exchanged a few emails about a year or two ago. At that time we were informed that you weren't taking on anyone else.

We are very much looking for a Showroom to rep us as we expand internationally, we believe we have grown into a brand that fits well with you guys.

Could we please set up a time to continue the conversation? We love the work you guys do.

Regards,

Carina Hardy
